**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Vitest scaffolding files are not source code. They are config that
# runs against the Vitest runtime, not the monorepo tsc build. The
# workspace lint ignores them; per-package `tsconfig.json` does the
# same. lint-staged is configured to only operate on package source
# files, so the root `vitest.shared.ts` is also outside its scope.
/vitest.shared.ts
**/vitest.config.ts
